{"tid":104174,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"黑絲李嘉欣孖老公十指緊扣　閃到爆！","createTime":"2017-02-02T01:07:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-02T05:12:10.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a9a7bac8bb9e34434480d47a228568d2a1cc7f52","tid":104174,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T01:07:36.000Z","msg":"「大美人」李嘉欣與老公許晉亨約在晚上7點半左右乘座駕抵達名人飯堂福臨門，出席許氏家族的飯宴，不過同行就未見兩人的愛兒Jayden（小JM）。着黑絲現身的嘉欣全程面帶微笑，與老公十指緊扣進入飯堂，兩人結婚超過8年依然恩愛，簡直羨煞旁人！&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而許晉亨的父母許世勳夫婦則在7時多乘坐另一部座駕抵達， 許世勳太太需由兩位傭人扶着慢慢前行。另外，許晉奎於7時到達。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170129/photo/bkn-20170129201737648-0129_00862_001_02p.jpg?20170130123050\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170129%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170129201737648-0129_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20170130123050&h=2210c3e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5dc1a3d4d7ae2b1db507138772486401ff8e83e1","tid":104174,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T01:10:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170129/photo/bkn-20170129201737648-0129_00862_001_03p.jpg?20170130123050\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170129%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170129201737648-0129_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20170130123050&h=a335a6c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b4a72d3ce37f15dd416009458ee033ad60b11949","tid":104174,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T01:10:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170129/photo/bkn-20170129201737648-0129_00862_001_04p.jpg?20170130123050\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170129%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170129201737648-0129_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20170130123050&h=922d91b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1fdea32ab715cfc8d8248c8c2a6148557d51f3